The taste is exceptionally sweet on the first sip, then it evaporates into a
completely vapid flavor devoid of any discernible taste but its sweetener blend.
It's exceptionally artificial and scarcely reminds of of Red Bull at all. The
sour apple taste of the OG it tries to imitate is just not there. Even
sugar-free Red Bull is more enjoyable to me and is more redolent of [[the
king|Red_Bull]].

